title: LUNAR ICONS NOT WORKING
body: RIOT, I have duo'd on every map more than twice and I only have the Trynd icon. What's wrong here?

replies.body: It took me a good few days after playing duo TT and ARAMs. Be patient!
Very helpful and swift assistance guys! My icons have appeared now. Thanks again!

You should get your icons no later than 3 days after the event ends **(February 15th 2014)**. If you did not receive the rewards after 3 days, please [let us know](https://support.leagueoflegends.com/anonymous_requests/new).


https://support.leagueoflegends.com/entries/25770895-Lunar-Revel-2014-FAQ
